    "(CNSS 2015 [80]) Traditional red-teaming might combine physical and cyber attack elements, attack multiple systems, and aims to evaluate the overall security posture of an organization.",
    "Penetration testing (pen testing), in contrast, tests the security of a specifc application or system.",
